        <text>
            <body><p>Noverint omnes presentes <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1 #A2" type="vacat" />
                            <rdg wit="#B">pariter</rdg>
                        </app> et futuri quod <persName key="d1e12540" xml:id="d1e133659">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A1 #A2">Radulfus</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Radulphus</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e12547" xml:id="d1e133666">Laurentius</persName> et <persName key="d1e12553" xml:id="d1e133669">Robertus, fratres de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324470" xml:id="d1e133671" corresp="Lucenay-le-Duc (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                                <app>
                                    <lem wit="#A1 #A2">Luceniaco</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#B">
                                        <foreign>Lucenai</foreign>
                                    </rdg>
                                </app>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName> quitaverunt domui <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e133679" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> usuarium et omnes calumpnias quas
                        antea habebant in finagio de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324488" xml:id="d1e133683" corresp="Émorots (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">
                            <foreign>
                                <app>
                                    <lem wit="#A1 #A2">Moraus</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#B">Moraux</rdg>
                                </app>
                            </foreign>
                        </placeName> de terris <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325011" xml:id="d1e133691" corresp="Sancti Martini">Sancti Martini</placeName>. Promiserunt etiam quod si aliquis
                        calumpniare vellet in ipso finagio fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e133694" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName>
                        <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1 #A2">garantirent</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B">guarantirent</rdg>
                        </app> eos ac defenderent. Et propter hanc quitationem, Fontenetenses
                        promiserunt eis in domum suam locum suum <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1 #A2">et societatem</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B" type="omission" />
                        </app> cum de seculo venire voluerint et in seculo quamdiu erunt tam eos
                        quam res eorum pro posse suo custodirent. Testes sunt hujus rei <persName key="d1e12559" xml:id="d1e133707">Hugo cellerarius</persName>, <persName key="d1e12565" xml:id="d1e133711">Odo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e133713" corresp="Grignon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                                <foreign>Grinun</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>, monachi de Fonteneto, frater <persName key="d1e12571" xml:id="d1e133717">Bernardus magister <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324489" xml:id="d1e133719" corresp="Morville (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Morville</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e12577" xml:id="d1e133722">Robertus major de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324421" xml:id="d1e133724" corresp="Bussy-le-Grand (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Buxeio</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e12584" xml:id="d1e133727">Renaudus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324449" xml:id="d1e133729" corresp="Étormay (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">
                                <foreign>Estormer</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>. Et ut hoc totum firmum permaneat et ratum, ego <persName key="d1e12590" xml:id="d1e133733">Willermus, abbas <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e133735" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        </persName>, presens scriptum sigillo <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1 #A2">meo</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B">nostro</rdg>
                        </app> roboravi. Actum anno incarnati verbi <num>
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A1 #B">m° cc° ix°</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#A2">milesimo ducentesimo nono</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </num>, mense aprili.</p>

                
